source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_00<tab>Houu is expert at weighing lesser evils against greater goods, and would see where you fit into the equation.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_00<tab>Houu aimerait que vous éliminiez un guerrier par<var 16 /var>ti<var 16 /var>cu<var 16 /var>liè<var 16 /var>rement vicieux.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_01<tab>Houu asks you to defeat Worr the Whalefin, a strategos in thrall to the Coral Tridents. Achieve victory in the FATE “Tail of a Whale” in the Sapsa Spawning Grounds to acquire Worr's coral band, and then present it as proof of your deed to Houu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_01<tab>Un guerrier sahuagin du nom de Worr a l'intention d'utiliser des subjugués comme chair à canon. S'il mène à bien son atroce projet, la guerre sera pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment inévitable. Houu veut donc que vous l'éliminiez, et lui rapportiez <var 33 ((Item)) 06F21E7C0202 /var> comme preuve de votre succès.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_02<tab>Houu receives the coral band and is greatly impressed by your martial skills. You have apparently made an equally strong impression on other Sahagin. Let us hope they will no longer be so quick to follow the Tridents' incitement to take on shorewalkers in open warfare...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez remis <var 33 ((Item)) 03F21E7C0202 /var> à un Houu très im<var 16 /var>pres<var 16 /var>sion<var 16 /var>né par votre courage. Il ne doute pas que la disparition d'un de leurs chefs fera réfléchir les Sahuagins à deux fois avant de reprendre les hostilités.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_TODO_00<tab>Deliver the coral band obtained in the FATE “Tail of a Whale” to Houu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_TODO_00<tab>Participer à l'ALÉA “La tentation du serpent de mer” et remettre <var 33 ((Item)) 03F21E7C0202 /var> à Houu à la Couvée de Novv

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Have you heard of the strategoi of the Shhhapsa Shhhpawning Grounds? They are leaders among Shhhahagin warriors, possessed of great influence.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_000<tab>Fsshhh, le terrible Worr s'est inssstallé au Frai de Sssapsssa, il a rejoint les Tridents du corail. On le sssurnomme le fanon d'acccier, et il sss'est conssstitué une petite armée de prisonniers sssubjugués.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_001<tab>Alas, the Shhhcarlet Shhhea Devil has been inflaming their pride with visions of easy victory. Shhhubtle and shhhly are the Coral Tridents. If nothing is done, their aggression will soon lead to all-out war with you shhhorewalkers...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_001<tab>Ccces imbéccciles vont trop loin<var 1D /var>! Imagine un peu la fureur des sssans-branchies sss'ils ssse voyaient obligés de tuer leurs sssemblables. Leur vengeance ssserait effroyable.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_002<tab>The strategoi must see that the shhhorewalker is a foe shhhkilled and dangerous. You will fight the most boastful among them. Worr the Whalefin is his name, and he must die this day. Pshhh...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_002<tab>Fsshhh, il faut absssolument élimnier Worr avant que l'irréparable ne sssoit commis.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_003<tab>Worr has a coral band, given him as an ally shhhworn of the Coral Tridents. Bring me this bauble as proof that Worr died as shhhamefully as he lived. Pshhh...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_003<tab>Rapporte-moi <var 33 ((Item)) 03F21E7C0202 /var> que les Tridents lui ont remis<var 08 ((<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C07 /var>)) ((e)) (()) /var> lorsqu'ils l'ont admis parmi eux, et je sssaurai que tu as réussi.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_010<tab>Pshhh... Shhhlay Worr the Whalefin and seize from him the coral band of the Tridents.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_010<tab>Élimine Worr le fanon d'acier au Frai de Sssapsssa et rapporte-moi <var 33 ((Item)) 06F21E7C0202 /var> comme preuve.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_011<tab>Pshhh... Worr's coral band, by all that's indigo! The clutchfather always chooses wisely... Little did I expect a shhhorewalker to best the Whalefin.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_011<tab>Fsshhh, c'est <var 33 ((Item)) 03F21E7C0202 /var><var 1D /var>! Pour être franc, je doutais un peu que tu puisses vaincre un guerrier aussi formidable. Tu es... sssurprenant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>.

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_012<tab>A strategos is a leader of minds as well as shhhpears. Worr's defeat at a shhhorewalker's hands is an object lesson that will shhhpread throughout the Shhhapsa Shhhpawning Grounds. Pshhh...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_012<tab>De nombreux Sssahuagins admiraient Worr. Qu'un<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> sssans-branchies l'ait vaincu les fera cccer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment réfléchir à deux fois avant de sss'en prendre aux gens de ta race maintenant.
